workers if they want it,' he added.
Meanwhile, the National Asthma Campaign, the Health Education Authority and
the Ulster Cancer Foundation are supporting a move by Action on Smoking and
Health (Ash) to bring a test case over passive smoking at work.
According to a legal opinion published by Ash, non-smokers may be able to
sue their employers for damage caused to their health by passive smoking.
