debate on Maastricht in Bonn.
Friday: UK, September retail prices index (up 0.3 per cent on month, up 3.5
per cent on year), excluding mortgages (up 4 per cent on year); Norway,
September CPI (up 2.3 per cent on year); Sweden, September unemployment
rate, September trade balance; Canada, September employment growth (up 0.1
